Source: linux-patch-@kernver@-mips
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: linux-source-@kernver@ (= @sourcever@), kernel-package (>= 9.006), debhelper (>= 4.1.0), module-init-tools, dpatch, bzip2
Maintainer: Debian kernel team <debian-kernel@lists.debian.org>
